### 2.5. Performance Optimization

- ‚úÖ **Performance-first approach**: Consider performance impact in all design decisions
- ‚úÖ **Optimize critical path**: Prioritize above-fold content loading
- ‚úÖ **Test Core Web Vitals**: Monitor and optimize LCP, FID, and CLS metrics

> **Reference**: See [Performance](technical/performance.mdc) for detailed optimization strategies. See [HTML Performance](../../html/html-performance.mdc) for image optimization and resource loading.

### 2.6. SEO Considerations

- ‚úÖ **Semantic HTML**: Use proper HTML5 semantic elements
- ‚úÖ **Meta tags**: Include descriptive title, description, and Open Graph tags
- ‚úÖ **Heading structure**: Use proper H1-H6 hierarchy (one H1 per page)
- ‚úÖ **Alt text**: Provide descriptive alt text for all meaningful images
- ‚úÖ **Structured data**: Use schema.org markup when appropriate

